title: Draft winners and losers
itunes:title: Draft winners and losers
description:
A room filled with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Conor Orr -- breaks down the 2015 NFL Draft, picking out the biggest winners and losers after the final selections are made in the Windy City. Elsewhere, Chris Wesseling and Kevin Patra call in from Chicago to deliver their first-hand impressions of the offseason's showpiece event.
